Feline van Aagten

I am a PhD candidate in the Lifespan Cognitive Dynamics lab and the Developmental Psychobiology lab at the Donders Institute.

My PhD is part of the Learning Variability Network Exchange (LEVANTE) project, which is a really cool global project on variability. If thats something you are interested in as well, feel free to send me a message!
